# AI Service (FastAPI) Rules
- Keep it small: embeddings, valuation, and assistant endpoints only.
- Type hints everywhere; pydantic models for request/response.
- Never call external LLM/embedding APIs without a timeout and error handling.
- Ground the assistant in real catalogue data (RAG) — never invent listings.
- Tests with pytest; every endpoint has at least a health/contract test.
